			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Tromelin Island’s Impressive Comeback</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">One small island in the Indian Ocean shows how quickly seabird populations can recover after people eradicate invasive predators.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/ethan-freedman/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Ethan Freedman</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
					<aside class="singlebydatewords singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Wordcount</h3>
						May 13, 2024 | 700 words, about 3 minutes
					</aside>

					
				</header>

				
